sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Aluno
    participant CF as CloudFront + WAF
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant ID as identity-service
    participant AS as assessment-service
    participant DB as RDS Postgres
    participant EB as EventBridge
    participant INT as integrations-service (Lambda)
    participant NOT as Provedor Notificacao
    participant AL as adaptive-learning-service

    Aluno->>CF: POST /assessment/{id}/submit (JWT)
    CF->>GW: encaminha
    GW->>ID: valida JWT
    ID-->>GW: claims OK
    GW->>AS: POST submit (correlationId=X)

    rect rgb(232,240,255)
    note over AS,DB: Transacao + Outbox
    AS->>DB: INSERT submission + INSERT outbox(AssessmentSubmitted)
    DB-->>AS: commit
    end

    AS-->>GW: 202 Accepted {submissionId}
    GW-->>Aluno: 202 Accepted ("recebido, corrigindo")

    rect rgb(255,233,214)
    note over AS,EB: Publicacao assincrona via Outbox poller
    AS->>EB: PutEvents (AssessmentSubmitted, cid=X)
    end

    par Correcao
        EB->>INT: trigger Lambda (correcao IA)
        INT-->>EB: publica AssessmentScored
    and Notificacao
        EB->>INT: trigger Lambda (notificar aluno)
        INT->>NOT: push/email
    end

    EB->>AL: AssessmentScored
    AL->>DB: UPDATE progresso, recomputa trilha
